    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single below-required factor (Test conditions, achieved 2 vs. required 3) is accepted given the regulatory precedent for single-offset ASTM F1717 testing and the conservative nature of the 60 mm offset. Overall model credibility is sufficient for the Medium model risk and Medium decision consequence context. Package note: a supplemental mesh-convergence study report was appended after original package signing to document GCI values formally; this evidence post-dates the package signature and has not triggered re-signing.",
